The paper deals with controlling a swarm of robots, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The use of spatio-temporal logic and mixed integer linear programming suggests a focus on optimization and control, which could also fall under machine learning (cs.MA) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the optimization of a metric, which could be related to systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the use of formal specifications and constraints could also be relevant to the field of logic and verification (cs.LG).
